---
title: Fuss-Free Tandoori Inspired Chicken Breast Traybake with Potatoes, Tomatoes and Yoghurt Drizzle
description: It only takes 10 minutes to prep this Fuss-Free Tandoori Inspired Chicken Breast Traybake. Prep the veg and marinate the chicken, then everything goes straight into the oven in for an easy dinner that gives you time back!
